- All right, well, I'll, uh,

29:18.032 --> 29:19.599
- I'll meet you guys there.
- Okay.

29:19.634 --> 29:20.967
- Okay.
- Bye, bitch.

29:21.002 --> 29:22.635
- Bye!
- [BELL JINGLES]

29:22.670 --> 29:25.271
[LAUGHS]

29:25.306 --> 29:28.074
Okay.

29:28.109 --> 29:31.811
[PHONE RINGING]

29:31.846 --> 29:33.246
Hey, Des.

29:33.281 --> 29:36.048
I was just calling to tell you
that I miss you

29:36.084 --> 29:41.454
and that I ran the entire salon
today by myself.

29:41.489 --> 29:43.489
You would've been proud. [LAUGHS]

29:43.524 --> 29:48.127
I... actually learned a lot today.

29:48.162 --> 29:51.197
See, before, I just thought
that your whole job

29:51.232 --> 29:53.566
was yelling at people

29:53.601 --> 29:56.636
and making fun of me
because I'm half-Asian,

29:56.671 --> 29:58.671
but now I know that

29:58.706 --> 30:01.874
there's a whole lot more to it
than just that.

30:01.910 --> 30:04.510
Being you is no joke, Des.

30:05.329 --> 30:08.047
So, hurry on back with your stankin' ass.

30:08.082 --> 30:11.083
[LAUGHS] Uh, uh, I'm just kidding.

30:11.119 --> 30:13.786
I didn't mean that. Uh, okay, bye, girl.

30:14.722 --> 30:17.390
- We need to talk to Chip.
- I've had enough of your shit.

30:17.425 --> 30:18.958
You said you didn't
want to talk about this shit

30:18.993 --> 30:21.327
'til Bryce was up... he's up.

30:21.362 --> 30:23.162
Are you out of your mind?

30:23.197 --> 30:25.998
You wanna go celebrate
your big brother's escape

30:26.034 --> 30:27.400
from the jaws of death

30:27.435 --> 30:29.769
by turnin' ourselves in
to the goddamn cops?

30:29.804 --> 30:32.139
Look, hear me out. We call Chip.

30:32.174 --> 30:34.040
We give him all we've got on
the Haitians and the Russians,

30:34.075 --> 30:36.175
- and then we skate.
- No. No, no, no!

30:36.210 --> 30:38.177
- I don't like any of that!
- I just saw them outside.

30:38.212 --> 30:39.512
I don't care! I said no!

30:39.547 --> 30:41.280
Chip's the only way
you're gonna stay alive.

30:41.316 --> 30:44.250
Us Hussers ain't ever been snitches.

30:44.285 --> 30:47.219
Fine. Forget it.

30:47.255 --> 30:48.354
Be prepared to look over your shoulder

30:48.389 --> 30:50.556
for the rest of your short life.

30:50.591 --> 30:53.377
You're getting on my last nerve,
boy... you know that?

30:54.796 --> 30:57.063
She said she was gonna kill
my baby, Clay.

30:57.098 --> 31:02.635
♪

31:02.670 --> 31:04.570
Kill my grandson?

31:04.605 --> 31:06.539
Yeah.

31:06.574 --> 31:12.078
♪

31:12.113 --> 31:18.684
♪

31:18.720 --> 31:24.991
♪

31:25.026 --> 31:27.093
[PHONE RINGS]

31:27.128 --> 31:28.704
Hey, Chipper?

31:30.098 --> 31:32.124
Wonder if you can meet me today.

31:33.701 --> 31:35.273
Got a little proposition.

31:35.308 --> 31:38.971
♪

31:39.007 --> 31:40.306
Have you heard yet from Desna?

31:40.341 --> 31:42.742
ZLATA: She must really be sick.

31:43.978 --> 31:46.212
Maserati has not left the house.

31:46.247 --> 31:48.047
Maybe you should pay her a visit.

31:48.082 --> 31:49.448
RUVAL: Yes, of course.

31:49.484 --> 31:51.684
I will check on Desna as soon as I can.

31:51.719 --> 31:55.421
Good. We have her exactly
where we want her.

31:55.456 --> 32:04.764
♪

32:04.799 --> 32:08.934
♪

32:08.970 --> 32:11.537
You okay? You look sad.

32:11.572 --> 32:14.707
You wanna come jump with us?

32:14.742 --> 32:18.144
I don't... I don't think
I know how anymore.

32:18.179 --> 32:19.345
Give it a try.

32:19.380 --> 32:21.881
Come on, it's your turn.

32:21.916 --> 32:27.119
♪

32:27.155 --> 32:32.391
♪

32:32.427 --> 32:35.528
♪ Cinderella dressed in yellow ♪

32:35.563 --> 32:38.330
♪ Went upstairs to kiss a fellow ♪

32:38.366 --> 32:41.267
♪ Made a mistake, kissed a snake ♪

32:41.302 --> 32:44.103
♪ Came back home with a bellyache ♪

32:44.138 --> 32:46.806
♪ "Mama, Mama, I'm so sick

32:46.841 --> 32:49.475
♪ Call the doctor quick, quick, quick" ♪

32:49.510 --> 32:51.844
MRS. WALLACE: Whenever you feel
it getting dark,

32:51.879 --> 32:55.514
just know you got a light
inside and it's burning bright.

32:55.550 --> 32:57.249
You know what? I should thank you

32:57.285 --> 33:00.686
for walking out on me, Mama,
'cause it made me strong.

33:00.721 --> 33:02.688
You let life take you under,

33:02.723 --> 33:05.424
but that won't be me... ever.

33:05.460 --> 33:07.059
Leave my brother alone!

33:07.095 --> 33:09.628
[LAUGHS] You suck! So does your brother!

33:09.664 --> 33:12.565
You don't need me to teach you
how to fight back.

33:12.600 --> 33:14.934
You've been fighting
since the day you was born.

33:14.969 --> 33:17.436
You don't talk to my brother
like that! You understand?!

33:17.472 --> 33:18.938
What are you gonna do about it?

33:18.973 --> 33:21.874
You were a shit-kicker
from a line of shit-kickers.

33:21.909 --> 33:23.876
[GRUNTS]

33:23.911 --> 33:28.147
You just need to remember who you are.

33:28.182 --> 33:32.885
Whoo! [PANTING] Y'all trying to kill me!

33:32.920 --> 33:34.220
Well, look at that.

33:34.255 --> 33:36.489
- We still got it.
- Never lost it.

33:36.524 --> 33:38.791
You're just gonna have
to turn that shit up.

33:38.826 --> 33:43.195
♪

33:43.231 --> 33:45.898
DEAN: Desna? Desna?

33:45.933 --> 33:48.200
D-Desna. Sor... I'm sorry.

33:48.236 --> 33:51.537
I-I didn't mean to startle you. Sorry.

33:51.572 --> 33:53.939
Let's get ready to go home, baby.

33:53.975 --> 33:55.784
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

33:57.311 --> 33:58.744
I gotta go make things right.

34:02.032 --> 34:04.366
It's so good to see you, Des.

34:04.778 --> 34:06.411
I was out of my mind earlier.

34:06.447 --> 34:07.779
I just thought
I was gonna lose everything

34:07.815 --> 34:10.248
and you know I didn't mean a word I said.

34:10.284 --> 34:11.882
You probably meant a few of 'em.

34:11.918 --> 34:15.053
[LAUGHS] Why are you wearing that?

34:15.089 --> 34:18.623
This is my armor. I can't
let anybody know what's up.

34:18.659 --> 34:20.092
I'm getting played, Jenn.

34:20.127 --> 34:21.226
Do what now?

34:21.261 --> 34:23.837
By Zlata and Gregory.

34:24.764 --> 34:26.431
My God, Des, that is awful.

34:26.467 --> 34:29.000
You were right. All this is my fault.

34:29.036 --> 34:31.603
- Now...
- Unh-unh. And I'ma fix this shit.

34:31.638 --> 34:33.538
But, first, I'ma talk to Clay.

34:33.574 --> 34:36.174
Until then, Gregory and Zlata

34:36.210 --> 34:38.610
cannot know that we are onto them.

34:38.645 --> 34:42.681
As far as they are concerned,
I'm just a blushing bride.

34:42.716 --> 34:44.815
You know I'm your ride-or-die girl.

34:46.018 --> 34:47.284
Don't you forget that.

34:47.321 --> 34:49.187
Yeah, you are.

34:49.223 --> 34:51.289
Yeah, girl.

34:51.324 --> 34:52.657
I love you.

34:53.226 --> 34:55.226
[SIGHS]

34:55.262 --> 34:56.895
Here he comes.

34:58.699 --> 34:59.798
Hey, what's up, Doc?

34:59.833 --> 35:01.399
- Hi, Jennifer.
- [LAUGHS]

35:01.435 --> 35:02.734
I heard the wonderful news.

35:02.769 --> 35:04.436
Yeah, thank you. It's so good.

35:04.471 --> 35:06.738
I'ma go check on Bryce.

35:07.708 --> 35:09.341
So, how are you doing?

35:09.376 --> 35:10.642
I heard you were sick.

35:10.677 --> 35:12.744
So much better now.

35:12.779 --> 35:14.479
- [CELLPHONE CHIMES]
- Ooh.

35:14.515 --> 35:17.616
Ooh. I gotta go.

35:17.651 --> 35:19.918
- Already?
- Mm-hmm.

35:21.321 --> 35:22.729
Oh.

35:23.924 --> 35:26.725
[CHUCKLES] Did you just bite me?

35:26.760 --> 35:29.227
You haven't seen my freaky side.

35:29.263 --> 35:33.632
Oh. I like it. You're bad.

35:33.667 --> 35:36.434
Baby, you have no idea.

35:36.470 --> 35:38.003
[CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

35:39.940 --> 35:43.041
DR. KEN: What's up, my man?
Commit any cool crimes lately?

35:43.076 --> 35:45.911
I hate my voice! Is that really
what I sound like?!

35:45.946 --> 35:47.712
- Unfortunately, yes.
- Oh, sorry.

35:47.748 --> 35:50.081
In all my years of working
these sting operations,

35:50.117 --> 35:52.617
you're the single worst
informant I've ever seen.

35:52.653 --> 35:54.019
I just had a question for you

35:54.054 --> 35:56.054
about the whole Witness Protection thing.

35:56.089 --> 35:59.925
Do Polly and I have to move
to a new state,

35:59.960 --> 36:01.860
or do we get the protection here?

36:01.895 --> 36:04.095
What makes you think
Polly's going with you?

36:04.131 --> 36:05.730
She's not?

36:05.766 --> 36:08.633
You're the only one working
on this case with us.

36:08.669 --> 36:11.336
That means you're going
to Witness Protection alone.

36:11.371 --> 36:14.105
But if we were married,
would that make any difference?

36:14.141 --> 36:16.992
Sure. But you're not.

36:18.111 --> 36:22.447
♪

36:22.482 --> 36:24.015
Hey. You look well.

36:24.051 --> 36:25.951
I heard you were under the weather.

36:25.986 --> 36:27.786
I'm better.

36:27.821 --> 36:29.254
So is Bryce.

36:29.289 --> 36:31.389
I am happy for Jennifer.

36:31.425 --> 36:34.626
I got my point across. Everybody win.

36:34.661 --> 36:37.596
I don't really give a shit
about everybody, Zlata.

36:37.631 --> 36:39.564
I care if we win.

36:39.600 --> 36:41.366
What are you gonna do about Clay?

36:41.401 --> 36:43.902
Don't worry. I've got a plan.

36:43.937 --> 36:46.938
Good. That man disrespected you.

36:46.974 --> 36:49.374
He deserves to be taught a lesson.

36:49.409 --> 36:52.377
[CHUCKLES] I like you agree with me.

36:52.412 --> 36:56.281
I got your back, Babushka.

36:57.751 --> 37:00.685
[CELLPHONE RINGING, VIBRATING]

37:00.721 --> 37:02.921
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

37:02.956 --> 37:06.091
Yes, Mr. Chip, what is the deets?

37:06.126 --> 37:09.394
CHIP: Clay just pulled off
the 301 by Enjoyment Land.

37:09.429 --> 37:11.713
He's almost here.

37:12.299 --> 37:13.999
Finish him.

37:14.034 --> 37:17.535
♪

37:17.571 --> 37:24.542
♪

37:24.578 --> 37:26.344
[DOOR CREAKS]

37:26.380 --> 37:27.512
♪

37:27.547 --> 37:29.447
[CELLPHONE BEEPS]

37:29.483 --> 37:31.549
[CELLPHONE RINGS]

37:31.585 --> 37:33.451
Yeah. Clay, where are you?

37:33.487 --> 37:34.819
Oh, we're just doin' a run.

37:34.855 --> 37:37.088
Do not meet Chip, okay?

37:37.124 --> 37:38.456
What?

37:38.492 --> 37:39.824
Do not meet Chip.

37:39.860 --> 37:41.226
- Why's that?
- Chip has turned.

37:41.261 --> 37:42.594
He's working for Zlata now.

37:42.629 --> 37:44.496
Clay? Clay?

37:44.531 --> 37:46.331
Shit.

37:46.366 --> 37:48.733
My man Clay!

37:51.204 --> 37:52.437
Chipper!

37:52.472 --> 37:54.372
Roller.

37:54.408 --> 37:55.707
[LAUGHS]

37:55.742 --> 37:59.678
So... what do you want to talk about?

37:59.713 --> 38:01.746
[LAUGHS]

38:05.152 --> 38:06.785
ROLLER: Holy shit!

38:06.820 --> 38:09.120
So much for going straight.

38:09.156 --> 38:14.893
♪

38:14.928 --> 38:20.498
♪

38:20.534 --> 38:21.700
♪

38:26.707 --> 38:31.288
♪

38:31.313 --> 38:36.282
♪ There's a brighter side

38:36.318 --> 38:40.954
♪ To every dark, dark cloud

38:40.989 --> 38:45.692
♪ And there's a smiling face

38:45.727 --> 38:49.763
♪ In every crowd

38:49.798 --> 38:51.297
♪

38:51.333 --> 38:59.272
♪ All your troubles will soon fade away ♪

38:59.307 --> 39:02.609
♪ If you look for the bright side ♪

39:02.644 --> 39:03.910
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

39:03.945 --> 39:08.014
♪ Instead of the gray

39:08.049 --> 39:10.950
♪ The rainbow in the sky Hello?

39:10.986 --> 39:13.173
Okay. I'll see you soon.

39:13.209 --> 39:16.756
♪ Will show the reason why

39:16.792 --> 39:19.893
♪ There's a brighter

39:19.928 --> 39:21.728
♪ Brighter side

39:21.763 --> 39:23.763
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

39:23.799 --> 39:26.232
♪

39:26.268 --> 39:27.600
Y'all okay? Yeah.

39:27.636 --> 39:30.537
I'm a wanted man, y'all.
This shit's suspenseful.

39:30.572 --> 39:33.440
Pol, you all right with,
uh, him staying here,

39:33.475 --> 39:35.175
'til we get this shit figured out?

39:35.210 --> 39:37.110
Yeah, as long as you don't
hog the remote.

39:37.145 --> 39:38.244
I gotta watch my stories.

39:38.280 --> 39:40.413
- "Children" or "Hospital"?
- Both.

39:40.449 --> 39:43.483
Good looking out, D.
Chip almost got the drop on us.

39:43.518 --> 39:46.352
Frankly, I'm surprised you even told us.

39:46.388 --> 39:50.955
I caught Zlata and Gregory
together last night.

39:51.393 --> 39:52.926
They've been playing me.

39:52.961 --> 39:54.928
Yeah, I'll say. Playing you how?

39:54.963 --> 39:56.629
In every way, Clay.

39:56.665 --> 39:59.065
The two of them are up to some shit,

39:59.100 --> 40:01.468
and I just gotta figure out what it is.

40:01.503 --> 40:04.337
I told you that Ruval was a
double-crossing son-of-a-bitch.

40:04.372 --> 40:08.074
Wait, wait. What?
What are y'all not telling me?

40:08.109 --> 40:10.510
What else don't I know, Roller?

40:14.549 --> 40:16.850
We made a deal with Ruval
to take out the Russians.

40:16.885 --> 40:18.885
And you've been sitting on that
this whole time?!

40:18.920 --> 40:20.820
- I didn't sit on it. I've been trying...
- No, no, no! No!

40:20.856 --> 40:22.689
You just wasn't gonna say nothing?!

40:22.724 --> 40:25.058
You was the one talking
to me about family!

40:25.093 --> 40:27.427
"We family, D!" Wow.

40:27.462 --> 40:28.795
You've been bitching and complaining

40:28.830 --> 40:31.631
about wanting to take the Russians out.

40:31.666 --> 40:33.122
You owe me.

40:35.203 --> 40:37.502
So, y'all gonna help me do it.

40:38.874 --> 40:40.874
But we gonna do it my way.

40:40.909 --> 40:43.009
♪

40:43.044 --> 40:45.278
[SIGHS]

40:46.481 --> 40:48.781
- D, wait!
- [DOOR OPENS, SLAMS SHUT]

40:48.817 --> 40:50.517
Hey, D?!

40:50.552 --> 40:52.018
Hey, D?!

40:52.721 --> 40:56.222
Oh, Lord. [LAUGHS] Why are you like this?

40:56.258 --> 40:58.391
- [GASPS]
- Daddy, we missed you!

40:58.426 --> 41:00.527
Hey, Daddy's baby! Come here!

41:00.562 --> 41:01.961
All right, let me capture this
moment, all right? Ready?

41:01.997 --> 41:04.898
Scoot in with Daddy Bryce.
Say, "Mani-pedis!"

41:04.933 --> 41:06.900
ALL: Mani-pedis!

41:06.935 --> 41:08.701
[CELLPHONE CAMERA CLICKS]

41:08.737 --> 41:11.304
- [LAUGHS] Hey, you guys.
- Beautiful.

41:11.339 --> 41:13.640
Hey, come on, tell me about school.

41:13.675 --> 41:15.542
You got your backpacks on.

41:15.577 --> 41:17.176
What'd you learn today?

41:17.212 --> 41:19.679
[INSECTS CHIRPING]

41:23.418 --> 41:25.985
[ENGINE REVS, SHUTS OFF]

41:26.021 --> 41:27.720
ROLLER: Hey, D?! D, wait up!

41:27.756 --> 41:29.088
D, sorry.

41:29.124 --> 41:31.424
You made a deal with him, Roller!

41:31.459 --> 41:32.926
Why would you do that?!

41:32.961 --> 41:35.562
I didn't make a deal.
I wanted to tell you.

41:35.597 --> 41:37.330
D, I swear, I wanted to tell you.

41:37.365 --> 41:39.132
But what?

41:39.167 --> 41:40.600
I had to protect Uncle Daddy.

41:40.635 --> 41:44.304
I get Clay's bullshit,
but I thought you...

41:44.339 --> 41:47.340
No, I thought we was better than that.

41:47.375 --> 41:49.976
[DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE]

41:51.780 --> 41:56.449
D, you right. You right.
You deserve better.

41:56.484 --> 41:58.751
I let myself trust him.

42:01.122 --> 42:02.388
But I guess, at the end of the day,

42:02.424 --> 42:04.891
you can't trust nobody
but your damn self.

42:07.762 --> 42:08.962
I'm sorry, D.

42:08.997 --> 42:10.930
Yeah, you are.

42:12.300 --> 42:16.703
♪

42:16.738 --> 42:22.241
♪

42:22.277 --> 42:31.618
♪

42:33.521 --> 42:35.788
[MAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ON TELEVISION]

42:35.824 --> 42:37.423
Pimento cheese on a cracker...

42:37.459 --> 42:39.759
that's a little slice
of heaven right there.

42:39.794 --> 42:41.127
[DOOR CREAKS]

42:41.162 --> 42:42.929
Yeah, it is. Hey, babe.

42:42.964 --> 42:44.564
What are you doing here?

42:44.599 --> 42:47.967
He's, um... He's gonna be
staying here for a little while.

42:48.003 --> 42:50.803
And due to the stress
of staying in these, uh,

42:50.839 --> 42:53.406
you know, sub-standard accommodations

42:53.441 --> 42:54.807
[LAUGHS] I'm gonna need me

42:54.843 --> 42:57.143
a little pharmaceutical assistance.

42:57.178 --> 43:01.681
♪

43:01.716 --> 43:03.016
Uh, can I talk to you for a second?

43:03.051 --> 43:04.884
Yeah.

43:04.919 --> 43:06.586
Pause it.

43:06.988 --> 43:09.422
Just, uh...

43:10.158 --> 43:11.424
[DOOR CLOSES]

43:11.459 --> 43:13.559
Look, I've been thinking
about this a lot,

43:13.595 --> 43:17.296
and I've decided...

43:18.667 --> 43:20.400
...I wanna spend the rest
of my life with you.

43:20.435 --> 43:22.802
Whoa, whoa! [LAUGHS] Whoa, Ken.

43:22.837 --> 43:23.803
Slow your roll, babe.

43:23.838 --> 43:27.173
What? But doesn't that sound nice?

43:27.208 --> 43:31.411
Look, you and I moving
to some small town somewhere

43:31.446 --> 43:35.314
and... maybe we could change our names.

43:35.350 --> 43:37.617
What? Why would we want to do that?

43:37.652 --> 43:40.920
Ken, you know I like this thing
we got going here.

43:40.955 --> 43:44.257
But I don't wanna move
to some small town with you.

43:44.292 --> 43:45.591
I'm... I'm finally starting to have

43:45.627 --> 43:47.994
the kind of life I always dreamed of.

43:48.029 --> 43:50.029
I'm a criminal, Ken!
No, no. Shh, shh, shh!

43:50.065 --> 43:51.597
And I am really good at it.

43:51.633 --> 43:53.066
- Shut up, Polly. Please.
- No, it's true.

43:53.101 --> 43:56.369
I got a whole bunch of male
escorts who look up to me.

43:56.404 --> 43:58.538
Now, they're my boys.

43:58.573 --> 44:01.007
Ken, they call me "Master Polly,"

44:01.042 --> 44:02.308
and I love it!

44:02.343 --> 44:04.610
And I understand that what
I'm doing is against the law...

44:04.646 --> 44:06.679
I know that... but it's my calling.

44:06.715 --> 44:08.014
I am a madam.

44:08.049 --> 44:10.016
[MOUTHING WORDS]

44:10.051 --> 44:12.085
[INSECTS CHIRPING]

44:12.120 --> 44:14.954
♪

44:14.989 --> 44:21.594
♪ When I am laid

44:21.629 --> 44:29.569
♪ I am laid in earth

44:29.604 --> 44:37.343
♪ Let my wrongs create

44:37.378 --> 44:38.978
[LAUGHS]

44:39.013 --> 44:43.883
♪ No trouble

44:43.918 --> 44:47.053
- Marry me, Desna.
- [GASPS]

44:47.088 --> 44:48.855
- [SCREAMING]
- [SCREAMING]

44:48.890 --> 44:49.989
Oh, my God.

44:50.024 --> 44:51.524
